│ instruction users of DeadVals into DeletedInstructions before dropping references and  │
│ removal, we satisfy the invariant and prevent the assertion failure. This aligns with  │
│ the delayed deletion design and with the pass semantics in the face of complex         │
│ reduction vectorization transformations."                                              │
